0000E8E6                         20706  ; ---- TRIGGER ROUTINES ----
0000E8E6                         20707  ; each one checks if already earned, if not it marks it,
0000E8E6                         20708  ; shows the popup, plays the sound and saves to file.
0000E8E6                         20709  ; they all work the same way just with different IDs
0000E8E6                         20710  
